summary: This document certifies the existence of NES, LLC, a New York Limited Liability Company, which filed its Articles of Organization on August 13, 1998. It notes that the Biennial Statement for the company is past due and is signed by N. Brendan W. Fitzgerald, the Executive Deputy Secretary of State.

persons.name: N. Brendan W. Fitzgerald
persons.context: He certifies the existence of NES, LLC and signs the document.

keyFacts: NES, LLC was established on August 13, 1998.
The Biennial Statement for NES, LLC is past due.
The document is certified by N. Brendan W. Fitzgerald.
